## Section-by-Section Implementation

### Section 1 — Hero
**Status: COMPLETE** ✅  
**Pattern**: Video background + gradient overlay

**Technical Specs:**
```tsx
// Video
- Source: /public/hero/journey.mp4
- Resolution: 1920x1080 (4.8MB)
- FPS: 24fps
- Autoplay: true, loop, muted, playsInline

// Layout
- Height: min-h-[90vh] (not full screen)
- Gradient overlay: from-black/75 via-[#5A0F14]/15 to-black/85
- Max-width: max-w-4xl
- Centered content

// Typography
- Title: text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl, font-bold
- Subtitle: text-lg sm:text-xl, font-medium, text-neutral-300

// CTAs
- Two buttons: Individuals (primary white), Professionals (outline)
- Height: h-12 sm:h-14
- Rounded-full
- Hover: scale-105 + arrow translate-x-1
- Icons: Arrow SVG with group-hover animation

// Scroll Indicator
- Bottom: bottom-8
- Animate: animate-bounce
- Opacity: opacity-50
```

**Design Rationale:**
- Video creates premium, cinematic entry
- 90vh shows user there's content below
- Gradient with Nevexa red touch maintains brand
- Large typography for impact
- CTAs with clear visual hierarchy

