### Section 2 — Why Import from Canada
**Status: COMPLETE** ✅  
**Pattern**: Accordion (Porsche-style)

**Technical Specs:**
```tsx
// Background
- Color: bg-white (contrast after black hero)

// Layout
- Padding: py-16 px-6
- Max-width: max-w-4xl (compact)

// Typography
- Title: text-xl font-bold sm:text-2xl
- Intro: text-lg font-medium sm:text-xl text-neutral-800
- Underline: h-px w-20 bg-[#5A0F14]

// Accordions (3 items)
- Structure: useState for active item
- Dividers: h-px bg-neutral-200
- Icon: + (rotation 45deg → × when open)
- Animation: max-height 0→500px, opacity 0→1 (0.3s ease-in-out)
- Title: text-lg font-semibold sm:text-xl
- Content: text-base leading-relaxed

// Hover States
- Title hover: text-[#5A0F14]
- Cursor: cursor-pointer
```

**Content:**
1. Recent Models (2021-2026)
2. Competitive Pricing
3. Verified History

**Height Reduction:**
- Before: ~800px (3 blocks stacked)
- After: ~400px (accordions collapsed)
- **Gain: 50%**

**Design Rationale:**
- Reduces visual clutter and scroll length
- Progressive disclosure keeps user engaged
- Porsche accordion pattern = premium feel
- White background = visual respiration after dark hero

