### Section 3 — How Nevexa Operates
**Status: COMPLETE** ✅  
**Pattern**: Timeline with image backgrounds

**Technical Specs:**
```tsx
// Background
- Color: bg-black

// Layout
- Padding: py-16 px-6
- Max-width: max-w-6xl

// Typography
