- Height: h-40 (160px fixed - uniform)
- Border: border border-white/20
- Shadow: shadow-lg shadow-black/50
- Hover: scale-[1.02], border-white/30, shadow-xl

// Background Images
- Each step has unique image in /public/process/
- Background: bg-cover bg-center
- Overlay: bg-black/75, backdrop-blur-[2px]

// Timeline Elements
- Dot: h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-[#5A0F14]
- Line: w-px bg-white/20 (connects dots except last)
- Number: White text inside dot

// Content
- Title: text-lg font-semibold sm:text-xl
- Description: text-sm sm:text-base text-neutral-200
```

**Images Required:**
```
/public/process/
  ├── step-1-sourcing.jpg
  ├── step-2-inspection.jpg
  ├── step-3-logistics.jpg
  └── step-4-customs.jpg
```

**Design Rationale:**
- Visual storytelling through images
- Timeline shows process flow naturally
- Uniform card heights = clean visual rhythm
- Background images make each step memorable
- Border + shadow creates depth on black

