### Section 4 — Brands We Source
**Status: COMPLETE** ✅  
**Pattern**: Marquee with logo cards + pulse animation

**Technical Specs:**
```tsx
// Background
- Color: bg-black

// Layout
- Padding: py-16 px-6
- Max-width: max-w-6xl

// Typography
- Title: text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] sm:text-2xl
- Underline: h-px w-20 bg-[#5A0F14]
- Legal note: text-[10px] italic text-neutral-600

// Marquee
- Animation: nevexa-marquee 34s linear infinite
- Pause: hover:animation-play-state-paused
- Loop: Logos duplicated ([...logos, ...logos])
- Fade edges: Gradient left/right w-16

// Logo Cards
- Size: h-24 w-36
- Background: bg-neutral-900
- Border: border border-white/20
- Shadow: shadow-lg shadow-black/50
- Hover: scale-105, border-white/30, bg-neutral-800
- Gap: gap-6

// Pulse Animation (Spotlight)
- Animation: brand-spotlight-pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite
- Effect: scale(1) → scale(1.15) → scale(1)
- Stagger: 0.27s delay between each logo
- Applied to inner wrapper (.nevexa-brand-spotlight)
```

**CSS Animation:**
```css
@keyframes brand-spotlight-pulse {
  0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
  50% { transform: scale(1.15); }
}

.nevexa-brand-spotlight {
  animation: brand-spotlight-pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}

/* Stagger delays for each logo */
.nevexa-marquee-track > div:nth-child(1) .nevexa-brand-spotlight { 
  animation-delay: 0s; 
}
.nevexa-marquee-track > div:nth-child(2) .nevexa-brand-spotlight { 
  animation-delay: 0.27s; 
}
/* ... etc for all 22 items (11 logos × 2 loops) */
```

**Logos (11 brands):**
- Mercedes, BMW, Lexus, Porsche, Tesla
- Audi, Toyota, Land Rover, Cadillac
- Hyundai, Honda

**Design Rationale:**
- Marquee = premium brand showcase
- Cards with borders = better definition on black
- Pulse effect = draws eye, feels alive
- Fade edges = infinite scroll illusion
- Legal disclaimer = transparency

