- Rounded: rounded-lg
- Link wrapper: <Link> wraps entire card

// Background Images
- Each card has fullscreen image
- Background: bg-cover bg-center
- Hover: scale-105 on image (duration-500)

// Overlay Gradient
- Normal: bg-gradient-to-t from-black/90 via-black/40 to-transparent
- Hover: from-black/80 (lightens slightly)

// Badge (Financing only)
- Position: absolute right-4 top-4 z-10
- Style: rounded-full bg-[#5A0F14] px-3 py-1
