- Icon: Arrow → with group-hover:translate-x-1
```

**Images Required:**
```
/public/paths/
  ├── individuals.jpg
  ├── professionals.jpg
  └── financing.jpg
```

**Design Rationale:**
- Image backgrounds make each path aspirational
- Overlay ensures text always readable
- Badge differentiates Financing clearly
- Hover effects feel premium
- Cards at h-72 balance impact with scroll length

