## Design System

### Typography Scale
```css
/* Headings */
- Section titles: text-xl sm:text-2xl, font-bold, uppercase, tracking-[0.12em]
- H3 (cards): text-2xl sm:text-3xl, font-bold
- H4 (accordions): text-lg sm:text-xl, font-semibold

/* Body */
- Standard: text-base sm:text-lg
- Small: text-sm sm:text-base
- Micro: text-xs

/* Special */
- Uppercase labels: tracking-wider or tracking-[0.12em]
```

### Spacing
```css
/* Section padding */
- Standard: py-16 px-6
- Dense: py-12 px-6
- Spacious: py-20 px-6

/* Max widths */
- Narrow (text-heavy): max-w-3xl or max-w-4xl
- Standard: max-w-5xl
- Wide: max-w-6xl
```

### Colors
```css
/* Backgrounds */
--black: #000000
--white: #ffffff
--neutral-50: #fafafa (very light gray)
--neutral-900: #171717 (very dark gray)

/* Brand */
--nevexa-red: #5A0F14

/* Overlays */
--black-overlay-light: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)
--black-overlay-medium: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)
--black-overlay-heavy: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)
```

### Effects
```css
/* Shadows */
- Card shadow: shadow-lg shadow-black/50
- Hover shadow: shadow-xl shadow-black/60

/* Blur */
- Backdrop: backdrop-blur-sm or backdrop-blur-md

/* Borders */
- Subtle: border-white/10 or border-white/15
- Visible: border-white/20 or border-white/30

/* Transitions */
- Standard: transition-all duration-300
- Slow: duration-500
- Ease: ease-in-out
```

---

## Performance Optimizations

### Images
- All images WebP or JPG, <200KB target
- Lazy loading: loading="lazy" on non-hero images
- Proper dimensions specified

### Video
- Single source (MP4) at 1920x1080
- Compressed to 4.8MB
- Autoplay muted (no audio track)
- 24fps (not 60fps) for file size

### Animations
- CSS animations (not JS)
- `will-change: transform` on animated elements
- `prefers-reduced-motion` respected

### Code
- TypeScript strict mode
- No unused imports
- Components split by section
- Content centralized in /content/en.ts

---

## Key Metrics (Estimated)

### Homepage Height Reduction
- **Layer 1**: ~6000px total scroll
- **Layer 2**: ~4500px total scroll
- **Reduction**: ~25% less vertical scroll

### Section-by-Section Gains
| Section | Before | After | Gain |
|---------|--------|-------|------|
| Hero | 100vh | 90vh | 10% |
| Why Import | 800px | 400px | 50% |
| How Operates | 500px | 700px | -40% (richer) |
| Brands | 300px | 300px | 0% |
| Choose Path | 1000px | 700px | 30% |
| Delivery | 700px | 600px | 14% |
| Contact | 800px | 600px | 25% |

### Load Performance Targets
- FCP (First Contentful Paint): <1.5s
- LCP (Largest Contentful Paint): <2.5s (hero video)
- CLS (Cumulative Layout Shift): <0.1
- TTI (Time to Interactive): <3.5s

