## Locked Decisions (DO NOT REOPEN)

1. **Mobile-first strict** - 390px viewport primary
2. **Porsche inspiration** - Premium automotive patterns
3. **No generic designs** - Every section visually distinct
4. **Layer-by-layer** - No jumping ahead to polish
5. **Content in /content/en.ts** - Centralized copy
6. **No forms** - Direct contact only (modal)
7. **Brand color #5A0F14** - Accent use only
8. **Black dominant** - With white sections for breathing
9. **Real Results disabled** - Until content available
10. **Desktop after mobile** - Complete mobile first

