## Technical Debt & Known Issues

### Current State
- ✅ No major technical debt
- ✅ All components type-safe (TypeScript)
- ✅ All sections responsive (mobile-first)
- ✅ Performance within targets

### Minor Items
- Hero video: Could add WebM fallback for better compression
- Brands marquee: Could optimize with virtual scrolling for 100+ logos
- Images: Could migrate to next/image for auto-optimization
- Accessibility: Some ARIA labels could be more descriptive

### Non-Issues (Intentional)
- No animation library (CSS only = performance)
- No state management library (not needed yet)
- No backend/API (static site for now)
- Limited breakpoints (mobile-first = 390px → 768px → 1024px)

